description: Littera Report is a platform for providing the best independent journalism in the world, and we work tirelessly to ensure that our contributors are able to develop and excel as writers and as professionals. We accept outside submissions from anyone, so long as the material is factually accurate and representative of excellent independent journalism.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Lit Report what is the top story today?
Alexa, ask Lit Report what is the top story in politics?
Alexa, ask Lit Report what is happening in sports?
name: Littera Report
shortDescription: Littera Report hosts the best independent journalism in the world!
